      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAZZLING DYNAMO (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at Ballarat in a handy 25.76 beating Geraldton Crew. Expected to be right there at the finish again. COLLINDA RAMSAY (1) was unfancied last time out but hit the ground running to lead all the way, scoring by 4.5 lengths (22.49) at Warrnambool in a Bottom Up - Maiden over 390m. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. IVORY RAMEN (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 425m behind Taltarni Lane (24.72) in a T3 Grade 6. Was in the money prior to that. Can figure in the finish. MISS HOOVER (3) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
